p>\r\n                <p className=\"text-purple-700\">\r\n                  Together we made the impossible possible!\r\n                </p>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </CardContent>\r\n    </Card>\r\n  );\r\n}\r\n"
